UNITED STATES of America, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Paul MASSILOTTI et al., Defendants-Appellants. No. 6543. Circuit Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. May 26, 1938.

Before SPARKS, MAJOR, and TREA-NOR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On motion of counsel for appellee, it is now here ordered and adjudged that this appeal be, and it is hereby, dismissed.
